ls that nice?

642
01:06:11,000 --> 01:06:13,434
- l don't want to play this game.
- Come on.

643
01:06:13,560 --> 01:06:16,279
- Please don't. l'm a model...
- You hands are so smooth.

644
01:06:16,400 --> 01:06:18,436
l don't want to play this game any more.

645
01:06:20,480 --> 01:06:24,029
lt really hurts!
