659
01:07:12,560 --> 01:07:15,028
George Lam?
Who's George Lam?

660
01:07:16,240 --> 01:07:17,195
Ching!

661
01:07:17,960 --> 01:07:19,598
Hello? Hello?

662
01:07:20,920 --> 01:07:22,990
George Lam?
Who's George Lam?

663
01:07:23,560 --> 01:07:25,630
George Lam? Who is Lam?

664
01:07:26,520 --> 01:07:28,351
- Who's George Lam?
- George Lam?

665
01:07:28,480 --> 01:07:31,790
