- l know you'll go back on your word.
- Have l ever not?

728
01:12:27,240 --> 01:12:28,878
So why did you drink it?

729
01:12:29,000 --> 01:12:32,117
l had no chance if l didn't drink it,

730
01:12:32,240 --> 01:12:35,869
and l may have a small one if l did.

731
01:12:36,000 --> 01:12:40,710
l drank it because of the small chance...

732
01:12:42,680 --> 01:12:44,557
Fung San...

733
01:12:45,360 --> 01:12:48,432
we've been brothers for many years.

734
01:12:48,560 --> 01:12:51,199
You know my personality well.

735
01:12:51,320 --> 01:12:55,108
l'd rather die than accept an insult.

736
01:12:58,360 --> 01:13:01,909
So far in my life,
apart from my parents...

737
01:13:03,080 --> 01:13:06,390
the emperor and our master...

738
01:13:07,680 --> 01:13:10,752
l've never bowed down to anyone else.

739
01:13:19,560 --> 01:13:24,076
l bow down to you now.
l beg you, let her go!

740
01:13:34,680 --> 01:13:39,356
You act like a piece of shit.
You've spoilt my interest in your girl.

741
01:13:39,480 --> 01:13:43,758
You lowlife, don't let me
ever set eyes on you again...

742
01:13:43,880 --> 01:13:45,711
or l'll kill you!

743
01:13:52,040 --> 01:13:53,758
Ching, are you all right?

744
01:13:54,320 --> 01:13:55,309
Ching...

745
01:13:55,440 --> 01:13:58,477
Sister, use this to bind your hand first.

746
01:13:58,800 --> 01:14:01,997
Sister, lead a better life from now on.

747
01:14:02,120 --> 01:14:04,714
There's something l have to do.
l must go now.

748
01:14:04,840 --> 01:14:07,354
Ching, don't go. Ching!

749
01:14:20,480 --> 01:14:22,789
Ching, what are you doing?

750
01:14:23,840 --> 01:14:26,479
Ching, where are you going?

751
01:14:27,760 --> 01:14:30,228
Ching, come back here!

752
01:14:48,880 --> 01:14:52,156
Hey, my horse!
Someone's stealing my horse!

753
01:14:52,280 --> 01:14:56,193
Medicine is very advanced now! There's
still hope if you go to the hospital at once!

754
01:14:56,320 --> 01:14:57,275
Ching!

755
01:14:57,800 --> 01:14:59,518
Ching!

756
01:15:26,880 --> 01:15:29,758
You stupid dog, using gold needles
to block the pulses!

757
01:15:29,880 --> 01:15:31,472
lf you force yourself to fight me,

758
01:15:31,600 --> 01:15:33,989
the poison will spread
to your heart in four hours

759
01:15:34,120 --> 01:15:35,917
and you'll bleed
from seven holes until you die!

760
01:15:39,640 --> 01:15:42,712
Why are you doing this?

761
01:15:43,640 --> 01:15:47,792
Blocking the pulses with gold needles,
l can keep my powers for an hour -

762
01:15:47,920 --> 01:15:50,593
long enough for me to kill you!

763
01:15:50,720 --> 01:15:53,154
Come and die then!

764
01:16:06,680 --> 01:16:08,318
Damn it.

765
01:16:24,360 --> 01:16:28,717
Come on, come on! Run faster
and pass them! Pass them all!

766
01:16:34,040 --> 01:16:37,032
Come on, stupid dog!

767
01:16:45,880 --> 01:16:47,836
Come on, come on...

768
01:16:52,840 --> 01:16:55,559
Fung San, l thought you knew me better.

769
01:16:55,680 --> 01:16:59,195
To keep my promise to the emperor
and protect my beloved,

770
01:16:59,320 --> 01:17:01,709
l wouldn't hesitate
to sacrifice my own life.

771
01:17:01,840 --> 01:17:04,673
Of course -
you're so noble, you stupid dog!

772
01:17:05,560 --> 01:17:07,949
Damn! Why is a car up there?

773
01:17:09,120 --> 01:17:12,157
lt's stuck... l don't want to know!

774
01:18:13,640 --> 01:18:15,471
l want you to die with me!

775
01:18:15,600 --> 01:18:16,919
You die first!

776
01:18:29,120 --> 01:18:32,430
Stupid dog,
you want to take me to the emperor?

777
01:18:36,000 --> 01:18:37,592
Shit...

778
01:18:39,680 --> 01:18:41,830
Where's the stupid dog?

779
01:18:46,320 --> 01:18:48,356
Where is he?

780
01:19:30,840 --> 01:19:32,831
Come and catch me, stupid dog!

781
01:19:34,240 --> 01:19:36,071
Faster! Faster!

782
01:19:41,480 --> 01:19:42,674
Hurry!

783
01:20:00,080 --> 01:20:01,195
Ching!

784
01:20:01,320 --> 01:20:03,072
Stop holding me! Ching!

785
01:20:03,200 --> 01:20:05,270
Rescue him! Quickly!

786
01:20:06,000 --> 01:20:09,709
The poison is working and l'm dying.
Goodbye, Sister.

787
01:20:11,640 --> 01:20:15,918
Ching, the doctors in Hong Kong
are excellent! They can save you!

788
01:20:16,200 --> 01:20:20,273
Miss, l'll ask you for the eighth time -
and give me a straight answer.

789
01:20:20,400 --> 01:20:21,753
Who is he to you?

790
01:20:21,880 --> 01:20:24,235
l'll tell you the same thing
if you ask a thousand times.

791
01:20:24,360 --> 01:20:26,794
He's my boyfriend,
Chief Royal Guard from the Ming Dynasty.

792
01:20:26,920 --> 01:20:30,196
- How dare you try to wind me up?
- You dare to hit me? l'll report you!

793
01:20:30,920 --> 01:20:35,710
l'll lick your toes clean if you can prove
he's from the Ming Dynasty!

794
01:20:37,640 --> 01:20:39,437
Doctor, is he saved from the poison?

795
01:20:39,560 --> 01:20:43,189
lt was carboxyl acid, but the sea water
diluted it and we managed to save him.

796
01:20:43,320 --> 01:20:45,880
l always say
Hong Kong doctors are the best.

797
01:20:46,000 --> 01:20:49,629
But something was very strange.
l conducted a cell analysis on him

798
01:20:49,760 --> 01:20:53,958
and it suggested he's over 300 years old -
which means he's from the Ming Dynasty.

799
01:20:54,080 --> 01:20:56,674
That machine really is no good.

800
01:20:59,440 --> 01:21:01,715
Aren't you going to lick my toes clean?

801
01:21:01,840 --> 01:21:03,319
Hey, why are you hitting her?

802
01:21:03,440 --> 01:21:07,035
Miss, do you want to report him?
l can be your witness.

803
01:21:07,920 --> 01:21:09,876
l just want to see Fong Sau Ching.

804
01:21:10,000 --> 01:21:12,833
He's still in a coma. The earliest
you can see him is tomorrow afternoon.

805
01:21:12,960 --> 01:21:16,077
You also have to get clearance
from the police.

806
01:21:19,200 --> 01:21:22,909
ln theory, you're not authorised.
But the police are compassionate.

807
01:21:23,040 --> 01:21:25,759
You're authorised this time.

808
01:21:31,840 --> 01:21:33,432
Sir, what did he say?

809
01:21:33,560 --> 01:21:35,710
Your boyfriend doesn't want to see you.
Leave now.

810
01:21:35,840 --> 01:21:38,559
- You're lying!
- Why should l?

811
01:21:41,280 --> 01:21:42,429
Hey!

812
01:21:43,520 --> 01:21:45,476
That really hurts! Let me go!

813
01:21:45,880 --> 01:21:47,996
OK, l'll authorise you one more time.

814
01:21:48,120 --> 01:21:50,156
But only for a moment.

815
01:21:50,920 --> 01:21:53,309
Ching! Ching!

816
01:21:55,800 --> 01:21:57,313
Ching?

817
01:22:00,800 --> 01:22:02,153
Ching, did you ask the police
to say you won't see me?

818
01:22:07,280 --> 01:22:10,955
Stop pretending you're asleep.
l know you're just pretending.

819
01:22:12,080 --> 01:22:14,310
l don't want to see you. Leave now.

820
01:22:14,800 --> 01:22:18,110
Have you gone mad
from taking ''The seven poisons''?

821
01:22:18,240 --> 01:22:19,673
l am Sister!

822
01:22:21,200 --> 01:22:24,237
You used me.
You've been lying to me all this time.

823
01:22:24,920 --> 01:22:28,037
You pretend to be a model,
but you're really a hooker.

824
01:22:28,880 --> 01:22:30,916
ln other words, a prostitute.

825
01:22:31,960 --> 01:22:35,839
A woman like you would have been
beheaded in the Ming Dynasty.

826
01:22:37,760 --> 01:22:39,671
Beheaded, my arse!

827
01:22:39,800 --> 01:22:45,238
l admit l was wrong.
l apologise. l know it was my fault.

828
01:22:46,120 --> 01:22:48,429
Won't you accept my apology?

829
01:22:49,160 --> 01:22:51,879
How about if l admit
that you're my boyfriend from now on?

830
01:22:52,000 --> 01:22:53,274
l'll be nicer to you.

831
01:22:54,760 --> 01:22:57,354
But l won't admit that you're my girlfriend.

832
01:22:57,480 --> 01:23:01,075
So why did you say you love me?

833
01:23:02,600 --> 01:23:06,752
lf l didn't love you,
would l be willing to die for you?

834
01:23:06,880 --> 01:23:09,713
But to die for love is a different matter.

835
01:23:09,840 --> 01:23:13,276
l could never be with
a woman as bad as you are.

836
01:23:15,240 --> 01:23:17,515
l'm a man of principle.

837
01:23:18,440 --> 01:23:21,113
Can you stop this?
Stop being so mean to me.

838
01:23:21,240 --> 01:23:24,915
l'm already begging you.
What more do you want?

839
01:23:25,040 --> 01:23:26,871
l can change!

840
01:23:27,240 --> 01:23:31,518
One's personality is determined at birth.
People don't change.

841
01:23:32,480 --> 01:23:36,109
l'm still acting as Chief Royal Guard
300 years later.

842
01:23:37,120 --> 01:23:41,511
Fung San is still the same psychopath
who rapes and murders women.

843
01:23:41,640 --> 01:23:45,076
l can't suppress my feelings
for an evil woman.

844
01:23:46,000 --> 01:23:49,231
But l can force myself
not to see her again.

845
01:23:53,520 --> 01:23:55,078
Go now.

846
01:23:55,200 --> 01:23:57,953
l'm very tired and l need some rest.

847
01:23:58,560 --> 01:24:02,997
Fine! Just pretend l never met you!
l can't believe you're so heartless!

848
01:24:04,720 --> 01:24:06,312
Get lost!

849
01:24:20,760 --> 01:24:23,558
- lt's you, miss.
- Sorry, sorry...

850
01:24:23,680 --> 01:24:29,357
- Does he know l made this for him?
- No. l told him what you asked me to say.

851
01:24:29,480 --> 01:24:34,429
l told him that he looked like my dead son,
so l make soup for him every day.

852
01:24:34,560 --> 01:24:37,393
- Please take it.
- l shouldn't, really.

853
01:24:37,520 --> 01:24:39,158
- Take it.
- Thank you.

854
01:24:39,280 --> 01:24:41,794
See you tomorrow. Thank you. Bye.

855
01:24:46,880 --> 01:24:49,917
You've dropped everything!
Let me help you.

856
01:24:54,240 --> 01:24:56,151
You broke her things!

857
01:24:56,280 --> 01:24:59,113
- Forget it.
- Are you blind?

858
01:25:02,840 --> 01:25:04,910
Sorry.

859
01:25:10,640 --> 01:25:14,030
- What is it?
- l just wanted to give you back the flask.

860
01:25:14,160 --> 01:25:17,835
- l'm not sure if it's broken or not.
- lt doesn't matter.

861
01:25:21,800 --> 01:25:23,552
Please take it. Take it.

862
01:25:23,680 --> 01:25:25,955
- Why are you giving me so much money?
- Take it.

863
01:25:26,080 --> 01:25:28,150
- Do one thing for me, please.
- What is it?

864
01:25:36,120 --> 01:25:37,758
Thank you, sir.

865
01:25:37,880 --> 01:25:41,316
He'll be back immediately
after the urine test.

866
01:25:46,320 --> 01:25:49,357
Don't say a thing. Fung San is here.

867
01:25:56,880 --> 01:25:59,633
Why are you covering your head?

868
01:26:30,840 --> 01:26:32,831
Damn it! Reverse that bad luck.

869
01:26:35,160 --> 01:26:37,720
is being exhibited for the first time
around the world.

870
01:26:37,840 --> 01:26:41,992
lt will be exhibited in Hong Kong
in three months.

871
01:26:42,120 --> 01:26:46,636
The Wheel of Life and Death
is more than 500 years old.

872
01:27:07,880 --> 01:27:11,236
Brother San, there are six boxes
and you've counted them.

873
01:27:11,360 --> 01:27:14,716
That's $488,000 altogether.
Let's see the money.

874
01:27:15,920 --> 01:27:18,878
You're buying a lot of guns.
Are you starting a war?

875
01:27:19,000 --> 01:27:22,754
lf you're planning a robbery, count us in.

876
01:27:23,960 --> 01:27:25,916
Damn you.

877
01:27:27,000 --> 01:27:31,630
l've thought it through.
l'll always be discriminated against here.

878
01:27:32,400 --> 01:27:36,188
lt's not my territory. l can't compete
with Hong Kong people.

879
01:27:37,280 --> 01:27:41,990
My expertise in martial arts
doesn't help me here.

880
01:27:42,120 --> 01:27:45,715
l'll take the guns
back to the Ming Dynasty,

881
01:27:45,840 --> 01:27:47,831
destroy the palace,

882
01:27:47,960 --> 01:27:51,589
kill the useless emperor
and crown myself in his place!

883
01:27:55,720 --> 01:27:58,871
Little brothers,
history must be rewritten.

884
01:27:59,400 --> 01:28:02,915
Brother San, that's too cryptic.
l don't understand.

885
01:28:03,040 --> 01:28:05,554
lt's better that you don't.

886
01:28:06,440 --> 01:28:08,795
lt won't do you any good.

887
01:28:10,240 --> 01:28:12,629
Any more national treasures arrived?
Anything interesting?

888
01:28:12,760 --> 01:28:16,594
Yes. There are 1 50 items.
Let me show you.

889
01:28:22,960 --> 01:28:26,157
A sword, hundreds of years old,
with no rust at all.

890
01:28:26,280 --> 01:28:27,998
The Dragon Spring Sword?

891
01:28:28,120 --> 01:28:30,509
Someone's willing to pay $180,000 for it.

892
01:28:30,640 --> 01:28:35,316
Damn. lt really is
Fong Sau Ching's Dragon Spring Sword.

893
01:28:35,440 --> 01:28:38,477
My sword was broken by this.

894
01:28:38,600 --> 01:28:42,070
This sword is worth 10 million dollars.
l'll have it!

895
01:28:43,600 --> 01:28:47,718
OK. Give me one million tomorrow
and l'll sell it to you.

896
01:28:47,840 --> 01:28:53,312
You don't deserve the sword.
You don't even know how to use it.

897
01:28:53,440 --> 01:28:55,795
Let me show you
how much it's worth.

898
01:29:00,600 --> 01:29:03,558
This precious sword really doesn't stain.

899
01:29:04,480 --> 01:29:06,675
What a sword!

900
01:29:23,000 --> 01:29:25,958
l'll rule the Ming Dynasty! l'll rule it!

901
01:29:27,040 --> 01:29:31,909
''The Wheel of Life and Death will be
exhibited in Hong Kong in two months.''

902
01:29:33,680 --> 01:29:36,069
Life is full of coincidences.

903
01:29:36,200 --> 01:29:39,670
The Wheel will be exhibited in Hong Kong.

904
01:29:39,800 --> 01:29:42,234
ls this really ordained in heaven?

905
01:29:43,240 --> 01:29:45,879
ln two months and 1 7 days at midnight...

906
01:29:46,360 --> 01:29:49,033
it will be the date
to achieve Buddhist enlightenment

907
01:29:49,160 --> 01:29:52,197
and the Wheel will hold supreme power.

908
01:29:52,920 --> 01:29:57,232
Fung San will surely act on that day,
and l shall complete my mission then.

909
01:29:58,080 --> 01:30:00,150
Are you confident you'll beat him?

910
01:30:00,280 --> 01:30:01,395
No.

911
01:30:01,520 --> 01:30:05,479
Then why do you want to provoke him?
Can you stop being so stubborn?

912
01:30:05,600 --> 01:30:09,309
l can't. l promised the emperor
l'd bring Fung San back for punishment.

913
01:30:09,440 --> 01:30:13,035
l'll be guilty of disrespect to the emperor
if l don't keep my promise.

914
01:30:13,160 --> 01:30:16,357
lf l can't beat him, l'll die with him.

915
01:30:16,480 --> 01:30:18,675
lf l'm fortunate enough to beat him,

916
01:30:18,800 --> 01:30:21,553
l'll take him back to the Ming Dynasty
through the Wheel.

917
01:30:23,520 --> 01:30:28,196
So you're leaving...
and you won't come back again?

918
01:30:29,280 --> 01:30:31,669
l don't belong here anyway.

919
01:30:32,440 --> 01:30:34,431
And what about me?

920
01:30:35,120 --> 01:30:38,874
- You'd better leave now.
- Have you gone insane?

921
01:30:40,120 --> 01:30:42,156
Didn't you say you love me?

922
01:30:42,880 --> 01:30:47,078
Love is a different matter.
l must train hard for the next two months.

923
01:30:47,200 --> 01:30:50,237
And l must also make a sword
to fight Fung San with.

924
01:30:50,360 --> 01:30:53,352
How can l concentrate
if you're staying here?

925
01:30:53,480 --> 01:30:55,869
lt's better to cut things short.

926
01:30:56,000 --> 01:30:57,991
As the singer Mui said,

927
01:30:58,120 --> 01:31:02,272
''Love is not meant to be forever.
Cherish it when you find it.''

928
01:31:03,800 --> 01:31:07,634
l don't care. l won't leave.

929
01:31:09,320 --> 01:31:13,279
Fine. Then prove that you can change.

930
01:31:14,080 --> 01:31:17,038
- How can l prove it?
- That's up to you.

931
01:31:19,200 --> 01:31:21,111
We'll see.

932
01:31:31,080 --> 01:31:34,595
Eat more - you never know
if you'll get struck by lightning.

933
01:31:34,720 --> 01:31:36,517
And l still outrank you.

934
01:32:19,400 --> 01:32:20,674
Hey.

935
01:32:48,800 --> 01:32:50,756
Delicious?

936
01:33:30,480 --> 01:33:34,393
Your Majesty,
your servant has made a strong sword.

937
01:33:34,520 --> 01:33:37,114
l promise you l'll defeat Fung San.

938
01:33:37,240 --> 01:33:40,994
Please give me strength from heaven
so that l can complete my mission.

939
01:33:50,200 --> 01:33:53,670
Ching, this bulletproof jacket
is for you.

940
01:34:19,760 --> 01:34:21,716
This sword belongs to you.

941
01:34:24,680 --> 01:34:27,148
''Sister's Sword''?
So it is mine?

942
01:34:27,280 --> 01:34:29,316
How cool is that?!

943
01:34:30,080 --> 01:34:33,470
There's something else.
Just wait a minute.

944
01:35:07,120 --> 01:35:08,712
Ching?

945
01:35:09,720 --> 01:35:11,551
Ching!

946
01:35:39,160 --> 01:35:42,118
What are you doing?
The exhibition hall is closed.

947
01:36:36,920 --> 01:36:38,478
''Fung San, you degenerate,

948
01:36:38,600 --> 01:36:41,717
fight me on the roof
if you want the black jade Buddha.''

949
01:36:42,640 --> 01:36:44,676
Stupid dog.

950
01:37:14,760 --> 01:37:16,318
Fung San!

951
01:37:16,680 --> 01:37:18,272
You're riddled with sin
and you've committed many crimes.

952
01:37:19,400 --> 01:37:24,554
Come back to the Ming Dynasty with me.
l'll beg the emperor to spare you.

953
01:41:13,200 --> 01:41:15,111
l'll blow you to bits!

954
01:46:36,160 --> 01:46:37,752
Ching!

955
01:47:27,960 --> 01:47:30,349
Ching!

956
01:48:05,520 --> 01:48:08,193
Now pay the money back, bitch.

957
01:48:09,440 --> 01:48:11,908
Don't call yourself a sister
if you can't pay it back.

958
01:48:12,040 --> 01:48:15,919
l haven't been a sister for a long time.
l work in a shop now.

959
01:48:16,560 --> 01:48:18,710
l don't have the money to pay you back.

960
01:48:18,840 --> 01:48:22,674
All l've got is $200. Do you want it?
l'll give it to you.

961
01:48:22,800 --> 01:48:25,075
Aren't you afraid of the acid?

962
01:48:32,640 --> 01:48:34,551
lt's just water.

963
01:48:47,720 --> 01:48:48,835
Ching!

964
01:48:49,960 --> 01:48:52,793
You're still alive? ls this real?

965
01:48:52,920 --> 01:48:55,309
This is great!

966
01:48:56,200 --> 01:48:59,715
This is sexual harassment!

967
01:49:45,680 --> 01:49:48,319
The End

